      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle has been curated for the most discerning enthusiast, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in an untouched state. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been rigorously vetted to ensure the asset meets the highest standards of preservation. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the typical pre-owned classification, offering an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
