    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, further protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the original factory floor mats are spotless, and it retains that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, it is flawless, featuring a complete service history from the local dealership and a recent comprehensive multi-point inspection. Every button, feature, and sensor functions perfectly. This is not just a used car; it is a specimen for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
