    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Turbo featuring the iconic 3.6L Mezger twin-turbocharged flat-six. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a 6-speed manual transaxle and a viscous-clutch all-wheel-drive system that remains tight and responsive. The engine features its original dry-sump lubrication system with zero seepage, and the twin K24 turbochargers provide instantaneous, linear boost. The chassis is preserved in its factory configuration, utilizing four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors for exceptional thermal management. Every component, from the suspension bushings to the synchros, operates with the precision",
